description: Stevedores plan to block the French port, preventing ships from entering the harbour.
title: Condor cancels Jersey-St Malo sailings due to port strike
title_page: Condor cancels Jersey-St Malo sailings due to port strike - BBC News
maintext: "We had considered using alternative ports in order to offer a service between the island and mainland France, such as via Cherbourg, but this is no longer an option available to us due to the threat of a blockade there too."
